<br>
Not trying to stir up trouble, just putting it in perspective. An epic for a 4 guild alliance is just as important to THEM as your epic is to YOU. Hell, I would almost argue that a 3 or 4 guild alliance taking down a dragon is more impressive than a single guild. Just imagine the logistical nightmare. Karadin has trouble getting OUR guild to listen, I shudder to think what it would be like with not everybody sharing /gu....<br>
